snippet.title: [Net Yaroze] The Incredible Coneman
snippet.description:
Net Yaroze was a PlayStation development kit for hobbyists, enthusiasts, amateur game designers... The games, which were usually small, were usually released on Demo discs, Official PlayStation Magazine being quite a big part in showcasing Yaroze games.

This is the Incredible Coneman, and it's a Yaroze game that isn't hard to control!

The game was featured on the Official UK PlayStation Magazine demo disc 15.
